<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 01 at 11:07AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Patchy dense fog likely to persist into early afternoon...
Patchy dense fog will persist across much of northeastern Indiana
into northwestern Ohio into early this afternoon. Highly variable
visibilities are being encountered with some spots near zero at
times. Conditions will slowly improve across northeastern Indiana
first early this afternoon and then slowly spread into
northwestern Ohio.
If you encounter dense fog, slow down, use low beam headlights
and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.</description>
